# VPS SSH Connection

**Always use the SSH config host** when connecting to the DIN COUTURE VPS or running remote commands.

## SSH Config (~/.ssh/config)

```
Host dincouture-vps
  HostName 72.62.254.176
  User root
  Port 22
  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/<your-ed25519-key>
  ServerAliveInterval 30
  ServerAliveCountMax 3
```

## Usage

```bash
# Connect
ssh dincouture-vps

# Run command
ssh dincouture-vps "docker ps"

# Run script
ssh dincouture-vps "cd /root/NEWPOSV3 && git pull && bash deploy-erp-domain.sh"
```

